<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It"&gt;18It Itivuttakapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/1"&gt;1 Ekakanipāta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/1/1.2"&gt;1.2 Dutiyavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;1.2.2 Kodhapariññāsutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Ekakanipāta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Dutiyavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Kodhapariññāsutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_61"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;12.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;61&lt;/span&gt;Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_62"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;62&lt;/span&gt;“Kodhaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Kodhañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā”ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_63"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;63&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Yena kodhena kuddhāse,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Taṃ kodhaṃ sammadaññāya,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pajahanti vipassino;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Pahāya na punāyanti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;imaṃ lokaṃ kudācanan”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_64"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;64&lt;/span&gt;Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="